NOTES:  Background: ANSER CAERULESCENS CAERULESCENS (DEEPER COARSER CALL);  Weather: WIND; COLONY SOUNDS, HIGHER NOTES, AND MOANING SOUNDS. GOOD INDIVIDUAL CALLS AT ABOUT 6:00.    This cut was noted as being a 7 1/2 IPS copy of a 3 3/4 IPS recording.  It was copied at the wrong speed however, so the recording still needs to be played at 3 3/4 IPS. JN 7 Oct 2005

ML: Background subject changed from recordist's original identification of Chen caerulescens caerulescens to Chen caerulescens to conform to eBird Taxonomy (v. 1.55). -Jay McGowan/Matt Medler, July 2015. Social Context: Colony.
